<h1>怀</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">huái</span><span class=alesi>(huai2)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">fù</span><span class=alesi>(fu4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 怀 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 怀</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/bosom" style="color:black;">bosom</a>, <a href="/dictionary/breast" style="color:black;">breast</a>; <a href="/dictionary/carry" style="color:black;">carry</a> in bosom</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 7<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 7 strokes: <a href="/character/我" title="wo3: our, us, i, me, my, we">我</a>, <a href="/character/这" title="zhe4: this, the, here">这</a>, <a href="/character/来" title="lai2: come, coming; return, returning">来</a>, <a href="/character/时" title="shi2: time, season; era, age, period">时</a>, <a href="/character/你" title="ni3: you, second person pronoun">你</a>, <a href="/character/作" title="zuo4: make; work; compose, write; act, perform">作</a>, <a href="/character/里" title="li3: unit of distance; village; lane">里</a>, <a href="/character/没" title="mei2: not, have not, none; drown, sink">没</a>, <a href="/character/还" title="hai2: still, yet, also, besides">还</a>, <a href="/character/进" title="jin4: advance, make progress, enter">进</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/心" title="Kangxi radical 61">心</a>&nbsp;61.4</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 4 <br><small>Other HSK 4 characters: <a href="/character/养" title="yang3: raise, rear, bring up; support">养</a>, <a href="/character/乱" title="luan4: confusion, state of chaos, revolt">乱</a>, <a href="/character/压" title="ya1: press; oppress; crush; pressure">压</a>, <a href="/character/免" title="mian3: spare; excuse from; evade">免</a>, <a href="/character/航" title="hang2: sail; navigate; ship, boat">航</a>, <a href="/character/优" title="you1: superior, excellent; actor">优</a>, <a href="/character/坚" title="jian1: hard, strong, firm; resolute">坚</a>, <a href="/character/著" title="zhe: manifest; (Cant.) to wear">著</a>, <a href="/character/降" title="jiang4: descend, fall, drop; lower, down">降</a>, <a href="/character/份" title="fen4: portion, part; duty">份</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-4" title="List of HSK 4 characters" 