ackground:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">懷|怀[<span style="color:#cc7700;">huái</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- bosom<br>- heart<br>- mind<br>- to think of<br>- to harbor in one's mind<br>- to conceive (a child)<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+6000</p></div>

